WEBVTT

00:06:28.147 --> 00:06:31.394
Six months later, they had
significantly higher performance,

00:06:31.418 --> 00:06:33.227
more satisfied customers

00:06:33.251 --> 00:06:35.385
and higher retention rates, too.

00:06:35.886 --> 00:06:37.346
Think about your job.

00:06:37.370 --> 00:06:40.177
How often do you have a chance
to use your strengths?

00:06:41.283 --> 00:06:43.255
Marcus and his team have surveyed people

00:06:43.279 --> 00:06:45.776
on whether they have the freedom
to modify their jobs

00:06:45.800 --> 00:06:47.514
to better fit their strengths.

00:06:47.538 --> 00:06:49.949
Lots of people say
they do have that freedom.

00:06:49.973 --> 00:06:53.402
But surprisingly few of them
actually do something with it.

00:06:53.862 --> 00:06:56.159
MB: Some people are
in the wrong job, I get it --

00:06:56.183 --> 00:06:59.417
27 percent of people probably
in their job feel totally constricted.

